#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/mSL6truNrWP1Bn9ng1rN0SkMI4f.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Dallas, a burdened but headstrong dancer, is determined to get into the best dance school in the country—her late mother’s alma mater. However, that dream is suddenly derailed when the cheeky yet secretly grieving football star, Drayton, crashes into her life with a unique story of his own. Will the two of them be able to grow into their dreams together, or will their dreams be sidelined?" year="2025-02-06" director="Justin Wu" actors="Siena Agudong, Noah Beck, Drew Ray Tanner, James Van Der Beek, Deborah Cox",Sidelined: The QB and Me (2025)
