#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/1QOJAXMGV3wMVM2CwvuJQRtiLx8.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="When French painter Pierre Bonnard met Marthe de Méligny, he didn’t know this self-proclaimed aristocrat would become the cornerstone of his life and work. From this moment, she became more than just a muse for the “painter of happiness”, appearing in more than a third of his work. Together, they reached their artistic fulfillment thanks to a colourful love, different from the standards of their time, nurturing the great mystery around their relationship. Based on a true story." year="2024-01-10" director="Martin Provost, Juliette Maillard" actors="Vincent Macaigne, Cécile de France, Anouk Grinberg, Stacy Martin, Grégoire Leprince-Ringuet",Bonnard - Pierre and Marthe (2024)
