#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/p7jyFWiLyHPttqYBFAlLJwtYTYH.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Reclusive gym manager Lou falls hard for Jackie, an ambitious bodybuilder headed through town to Las Vegas in pursuit of her dream. But their love ignites violence, pulling them deep into the web of Lou’s criminal family." year="2024-03-07" director="Rose Glass, Susan E. Fiore, Peter Lyons Collister, Scott Rorie, Chemen A. Ochoa" actors="Kristen Stewart, Katy O'Brian, Ed Harris, Dave Franco, Jena Malone",Love Lies Bleeding (2024)
