http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1324743.mkv&play_token=3jUrQh806U&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/5ExAJJJfixiLalZ4Vevqz1i9G8.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="A French couple burnt out by the routine of their daily family life decides after much hesitation to travel to Sicily for a short holiday. Voyages en Italie depicts the neuroses and eccentricities of Jean-Philippe and Sophie, the gracious dynamics of their relationship and the depth of their affection and intimacy." year="2023-03-29" director="Sophie Letourneur" actors="Sophie Letourneur, Philippe Katerine, Guillemette Coutellier, Mahault Mollaret, Philippe Letourneur",Voyages en Italie (2023)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1324754.mkv&play_token=E3iICqF22V&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/7RzpN4aLjM5FUc7Q3WsvNn2MuaR.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Young Cole Carter dreams of hitting the big time as a Hollywood disc jockey, spending his days and nights hanging with buddies and working on the one track that will set the world on fire. Opportunity comes knocking when he meets James Reed, a charismatic DJ who takes the 23-year-old under his wing. Soon, his seemingly clear path to success gets complicated when he starts falling for his mentor's girlfriend, jeopardizing his new friendship and the future he seems destined to fulfill." year="2015-08-26" director="Max Joseph" actors="Zac Efron, Wes Bentley, Emily Ratajkowski, Jonny Weston, Shiloh Fernandez",We Are Your Friends (2015)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1324755.mkv&play_token=AJ2tlWu0sp&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/wcs8V1xIfSTdYKHAiazFWQfhPVD.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Afghanistan fell into the hands of the Taliban due to the withdrawal of US troops in August 2021. Upon hearing this news in a foreign country, the Makhmalbaf family rolled up their sleeves and set out to rescue Afghan artists in crisis." year="2023-10-06" director="Hana Makhmalbaf" actors="N/A",The List (2023)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1322674.mkv&play_token=NG8UtR9VPU&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/6re5NBRLemS5Ysvc60mGUGHz8C6.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Dans une banlieue populaire de Dakar, les ouvriers d’un chantier, sans salaire depuis des mois, décident de quitter le pays par l’océan pour un avenir meilleur. Parmi eux se trouve Souleiman, qui laisse derrière lui celle qu'il aime, Ada, promise à un autre homme. Quelques jours après le départ en mer des garçons, un incendie dévaste la fête de mariage d’Ada et de mystérieuses fièvres s'emparent des filles du quartier. Issa, jeune policier, débute une enquête, loin de se douter que les esprits des noyés sont revenus. Si certains viennent réclamer vengeance, Souleiman, lui, est revenu faire ses adieux à Ada." year="2019-10-02" director="Mati Diop" actors="Mame Bineta Sane, Ibrahima Traore, Amadou Mbow, Fatou Sougou, Aminata Kane, Babacar Sylla, Mariama Gassama, Abdou Balde, Coumba Dieng, Ibrahima Mbaye",FR - Atlantique (2019)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1319713.mkv&play_token=XSIYOYNuWv&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/2cLbyVNhEEaUJGg7rfbLtX6454I.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Shortly after David Abbott moves into his new San Francisco digs, he has an unwelcome visitor on his hands: winsome Elizabeth Masterson, who asserts that the apartment is hers -- and promptly vanishes. When she starts appearing and disappearing at will, David thinks she's a ghost, while Elizabeth is convinced she's alive." year="2005-09-16" director="Mark Waters, Benjamin Rosenberg, Janna Stern, Eric A. Pot, Robert 'Skid' Skidmore" actors="Reese Witherspoon, Mark Ruffalo, Donal Logue, Dina Spybey-Waters, Ben Shenkman",Just Like Heaven (2005)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1319731.mkv&play_token=ht6qkFxRfw&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/z13I3sWzOoKBDAEpJ7iK9bSznQn.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="The sexy Gin is the new love of Hache, but this can not forget his former girlfriend, so the love triangle is inevitable." year="2012-06-22" director="Fernando González Molina" actors="Mario Casas, Clara Lago, María Valverde, Álvaro Cervantes, Diego Martín, Marina Salas, Cristina Plazas, Nerea Camacho, Marcel Borràs, Carles Francino",FR - I Want You (2012)
