http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1289076.mkv&play_token=i54UBLLGI4&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/vBOioZKaGacNtx8G7qZeTPqemk7.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="Diane is a well-known lawyer, divorced for three years. She loses her mobile telephone and receives a call from the person who finds it. That person is Alexandre, a charming man and the perfect gentleman. They make a connection over the phone and agree to meet up the following day. But when Alexandre arrives, there's a surprise in store when Diane discovers he is only 4' 6' tall. From that moment on, Diane tries to overcome the prejudices of society and her own fears to experience the best time of her life..." year="2016-05-04" director="Laurent Tirard" actors="Jean Dujardin, Virginie Efira, Cédric Kahn, César Domboy, Stéphanie Papanian",Up for Love (2016)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1289090.mkv&play_token=kRPglmqZdY&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/tFuMLNU3IeWvNMaasJwsDkqbR3T.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="A la fin des années soixante, deux familles émigrent en Israël et se retrouvent voisines dans un minuscule village perdu au milieu de nulle part. L'une vient du Maroc et l'autre de l'Inde. Hormis un rêve, ces gens n'ont rien en commun.  Loin de leurs habitudes et de leurs influences culturelles, ils tentent de reconstruire leur monde. Obligées de cohabiter, les deux communautés se jaugent et tentent d'exister par ce qui les différencie. De malentendus en préjugés, la route vers l'harmonie s'annonce aussi tortueuse que surprenante." year="2004-06-06" director="Avi Nesher" actors="Liraz Charhi, Netta Garti, Jean Benguigui, Parmeet Sethi, Krutika Desai Khan, Ruby Porat Shoval, Nati Ravitz, Aure Atika, Rotem Abuhab, Israel Katorza",FR - Au bout du monde à gauche (2004)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1276511.mp4&play_token=2oGGgNaEmd&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/7InKwVFgvIgfwuPKd0C3R9OeoN7.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="As a patriarchal family yearns for the birth of a son to continue their family line, their youngest son secretly joins an erotic dance theatre and falls for its transgender starlet." year="2022-11-18" director="Saim Sadiq, Sana Jafri, Hyra Basit, Qasim Abbas, Tashish Habib" actors="Ali Junejo, Rasti Farooq, Alina Khan, Sarwat Gilani, Salmaan Peerzada",Joyland (2022)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1276522.mkv&play_token=jSTgbQyt8U&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/gcR1Ce6f2gqRxk2WjzRiparANjf.jpg" group-title="|FR| DRAME/ROMANCE" tvg-type="movie" description="When she fails to meet an item on his list of requirements for a bride, Julia Thistlewaite is jilted by London’s most eligible bachelor, Mr. Malcolm. Feeling humiliated and determined to exact revenge, she convinces her friend Selina Dalton to play the role of his ideal match. Soon, Mr. Malcolm wonders whether he’s found the perfect woman...or the perfect hoax." year="2022-07-01" director="Emma Holly Jones, Jill Dempsey, Stephen Fuller, Christine Dilworth, Ross Ferguson" actors="Freida Pinto, Ṣọpẹ́ Dìrísù, Zawe Ashton, Oliver Jackson-Cohen, Theo James",Mr. Malcolm's List (2022)
