#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/1luaxuRCI7X8mtNMKsQ4grBYICo.jpg" group-title="|FR| PRIME +" tvg-type="movie" description="A young woman is driving through the desert alone when she is drawn into a dangerous game of cat and mouse with a psychopathic Sheriff. The chase escalates to deadly levels, and she must use her street-smarts to turn the tables against him." year="2024-12-11" director="Lawrence Jacomelli" actors="Britni Camacho, John Schwab, Sydney Brumfield, Travis Lincoln Cox, Felix Merback",Blood Star (2024)
