#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/cjcrkPeQkrkEVYrd3lHWJbfBdrv.jpg" group-title="|FR| NETFLIX JEUNESSE FAMILLE" tvg-type="movie" description="Living a bleak existence at a London orphanage, 12-year-old Peter finds himself whisked away to the fantastical world of Neverland. Adventure awaits as he meets new friend James Hook and the warrior Tiger Lily. They must band together to save Neverland from the ruthless pirate Blackbeard. Along the way, the rebellious and mischievous boy discovers his true destiny, becoming the hero forever known as Peter Pan." year="2015-09-24" director="Joe Wright" actors="Levi Miller, Garrett Hedlund, Hugh Jackman, Amanda Seyfried, Rooney Mara, Nonso Anozie, Kathy Burke, Adeel Akhtar, Cara Delevingne, Paul Kaye",FR - Pan  (2015)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=289633.mkv&play_token=iDrRrowqvl&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/mYpEbF8FrAzk5aLcdC5U8dQQBRR.jpg" group-title="|FR| NETFLIX JEUNESSE FAMILLE" tvg-type="movie" description="Un bol de nouilles fumant de souvenirs, le nouveau souffle d'une beauté sur le déclin, la réapparition d'un premier amour. Trois contes de la vie en Chine urbaine…" year="2018-08-04" director="Yoshitaka Takeuch, Xiaoxing Yi, Li Haoling" actors="Taito Ban, Mariya Ise, Minako Kotobuki, Haruka Shiraishi, Hiroki Yasumoto, Takeo Otsuka, Ikumi Hasegawa, Crispin Freeman, Kendall Gimbi, Evan Rachel Wood",FR - Flavors of Youth (2018)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=287419.mkv&play_token=lv7Rnu4fJz&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/hehlwNM5Lpzo7ndkint6RnpQGeo.jpg" group-title="|FR| NETFLIX JEUNESSE FAMILLE" tvg-type="movie" description="En digne fils de son père, Luca décide d'aller sauver sa mère des griffes d'Erebos le Fou, mais il lui faut d'abord trouver l'élu capable de brandir l'épée Zénithienne. Une adaptation en images de synthèses du cinquième volet de la saga vidéo ludique Dragon Quest." year="2019-08-02" director="Ryuichi Yagi, Takashi Yamazaki" actors="Takeru Satoh, Kasumi Arimura, Haru, Kentaro Sakaguchi, Takayuki Yamada, Kendo Kobayashi, Ken Yasuda, Suzuki Matsuo, Koichi Yamadera, Chikako Kaku",FR - Dragon Quest: Your Story (2019)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=272851.mkv&play_token=f8jFGV40Uw&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/qb0eCUtvi2Rn5etdqFbaYzvIPYn.jpg" group-title="|FR| NETFLIX JEUNESSE FAMILLE" tvg-type="movie" description="Un facteur égoïste et un fabricant de jouets solitaire forgent une amitié improbable, apportant la joie à une bourgade sombre et froide qui en a désespérément besoin." year="2019-11-08" director="Sergio Pablos" actors="Jason Schwartzman, J.K. Simmons, Rashida Jones, Joan Cusack, Norm Macdonald, Will Sasso, Sergio Pablos, Mila Brener, Neda Margrethe Labba, Sydney Brower",FR - Klaus (2019)
