#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/jdg3ZxfRDPudWpy6FFxyKfw7q8F.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="Norvège, décembre 1942. Sarah et Daniel, jeunes enfants juifs, tentent d'échapper à la Milice locale et à la déportation en se cachant dans la cave des parents de l’intrépide Gerda, 10 ans, et d’Otto, 13 ans. Mais lorsque leurs parents sont arrêtés la veille de Noël, les deux enfants vont aider Sarah et Daniel à fuir vers la Suède, en pays neutre.  Ils devront affronter de nombreux périls et fuir les nazis lancés à leur poursuite avant d'arriver au bout du voyage." year="2020-02-14" director="Johanne Helgeland" actors="Anna Sofie Skarholt, Bo Lindquist-Ellingsen, Samson Steine, Bianca Ghilardi-Hellesten, Henrik Siger Woldene, Luke Neite, Julius Robin Weigel, Kari Simonsen, Morten Svartveit, Thea Borring Lande",FR - The Crossing  (2020)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=566116.mkv&play_token=2ICgBShyI6&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/d8drBimtE0UFLlIh8BrLyk0C8Ad.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="Follows a soldier trying to gain recognition for comrades who died in 1948, at a turning point in the civil war between the communists and the nationalist forces of the Kuomintang (KMT)." year="2007-10-09" director="Feng Xiaogang" actors="Zhang Hanyu, Ren Quan, Baoqiang Wang, Deng Chao, Yuan Wenkang, Tang Yan, Li Naiwen, Hu Jun, Fu Heng, Liao Fan",FR - Assembly  (2007)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=559235.mkv&play_token=mDKBL8McnU&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/6ctXBO0o5fKQvGdSJsPc8TAYCvp.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="A squad of the Jiaolong Commando Unit - Sea Dragon, a spec ops team of the Chinese Navy, carries out a hostage rescue operation in the nation of Yewaire, on the Arabian Peninsula, and fiercely fights against local rebel groups and Zaka, a terrorist organization." year="2018-02-16" director="Dante Lam" actors="Zhang Yi, Johnny Huang, Hai Qing, Du Jiang, Jiang Luxia, Sanaa Alaoui, Yin Fang, Yutian Wang, Guo Jiahao, Henry Prince Mak",FR - Operation Red Sea  (2018)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=559364.mkv&play_token=OUtmO7MnFs&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/r7dWdjimGZP2TFShQbyLm8eDJqS.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="A young man Kentaro Saeki keeps failing his bar test and does not know what to do any more. His older sister Keiko is a freelance writer. Kentaro and Keiko begin to search for information on their grandfather Kyuzo Miyabe who dead in the special  forces during World War II.  Their grandfather Kyuzo Miyabe was terrified of death and obsessed with life. Why did he join the special forces? According to his fellow navy soldiers, Kyuzo Miyabe was a genius and also a coward. Kentaro and Keiko then discovers the shocking truth which has been sealed for 60 years." year="2013-12-20" director="Takashi Yamazaki" actors="Junichi Okada, Haruma Miura, Mao Inoue, Isao Natsuyagi, Jun Fubuki, Kazue Fukiishi, Hirofumi Arai, Gaku Hamada, Yuuki Furukawa, Tatsuya Ueda",FR - The Eternal Zero  (2013)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=559260.mkv&play_token=abEMDzZUTB&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/7NVgVX663tdareijAiv0eLiLn6d.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="A Westerner finds refuge with a group of women in a church during Japan's rape of Nanking in 1937. Posing as a priest, he attempts to lead the women to safety." year="2011-12-15" director="Zhang Yimou" actors="Christian Bale, Ni Ni, Tong Dawei, Zhang Xinyi, Shigeo Kobayashi, Atsuro Watabe, Shawn Dou, Paul Schneider, Cao Kefan, Huang Tianyuan",FR - The Flowers of War (2011)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=559381.mkv&play_token=kAQocUYRZz&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/6b6tqchq0ELFwEqCAQKpglxEDi6.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="During the warring period of the three kingdoms, ancient China is in turmoil. To unify the country, general Cao Cao (Jiang Wen), the real power behind the Emperor, enlists the aid of the greatest warrior in the land, Guan Yu (Donnie Yen). However, Guan Yu is a loyal friend of Cao Cao's enemy Liu Bei (Alex Fong) so to persuade the peerless warrior to fight, Cao Cao takes his beloved Qi Lan (Sun Li) hostage. After leading Cao Cao's forces to victory Guan Yu sets out with Qi Lan to rejoin Liu Bei. But now Cao Cao has deemed him too great a threat to live, and on the journey he must face all the forces at the Emperor's command sent to destroy him." year="2011-04-28" director="Alan Mak, Felix Chong Man-Keung" actors="Donnie Yen, Jiang Wen, Sun Li, Alex Fong, Shao Bing, Andy On, Wang Xuebing, Wang Bo-Chieh, Dong Yong, Li Zonghan",FR - The Lost Bladesman  (2011)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=559424.mkv&play_token=qObgPPOfcf&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/oPlNLXkMFWryGh1P3nA7EIHIQ2n.jpg" group-title="|FR| GUERRE" tvg-type="movie" description="Un soldat américain quitte l'amour de sa vie pour infiltrer les lignes allemandes et tuer Hitler. Des décennies plus tard, ce dernier est confronté à un tout autre ennemi, un authentique Bigfoot issu des montagnes canadiennes." year="2019-02-08" director="Robert D. Krzykowski" actors="Sam Elliott, Aidan Turner, Caitlin Fitzgerald, Rizwan Manji, Larry Miller, Ron Livingston, Nikolai Tsankov, Ellar Coltrane, Sean Bridgers, Kelley Curran",FR - The Man Who Killed Hitler and Then the Bigfoot  (2019)
