#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/n70H9pmMzA8QNtd08E6knF6TjFl.jpg" group-title="|FR| FILM 1980-1999" tvg-type="movie" description="From the star and director of 'The Storm Riders' come this turbo- charged action drama. Pop superstar Ekin Cheng is Sky, an underground drag car racer king. After winning yet another race, Sky was framed by his rival Hung (Simon Yam). On the run in Thailand, Sky hooks up with his long lost father, himself a legendary racer, who steers his son back on course for the ultimate showdown with Hung." year="1999-12-18" director="Andrew Lau" actors="Ekin Cheng Yee-Kin, Cecilia Cheung, Kelly Lin, Blacky Ko Shou-Liang, Simon Yam, Patrick Tam, Jerry Lamb Hiu-Fung, Moses Chan, Stephanie Che, Samuel Leung Cheuk-Moon",FR - The Legend of Speed  (1999)
