http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=1438636.mkv&play_token=kVFDQteWOy&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/jf3YO8hOqGHCupsREf5qymYq1n.jpg" group-title="|FR| THEATRE ET SPECTACLE" tvg-type="movie" description="The cultural phenomenon continues on the big screen! Immerse yourself in this once-in-a-lifetime concert film experience with a breathtaking, cinematic view of the history-making tour." year="2023-10-13" director="Kelly Hernacki, Sam Wrench, Lizz Zanin, Tori Rose, Rita Cossette" actors="Taylor Swift, Mike Meadows, Max Bernstein, Paul Sidoti, Amos Heller",FR - TAYLOR SWIFT | THE ERAS TOUR (2023)
